					<img src="../images/rl_style_guide2_title.gif" alt="RL STYLE GUIDE" />
					<p>In addition to choosing a font, you may choose a two- or three-initial monogram format. 
						In our monogram choices, A is the first name, B is the middle and C is the last name.</p>
					<h3>AC monogram (all fonts):</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>The AC model consists of your first (A) and last (C) name, with A and C the same size.</li>
					</ul>
					<h3>ABC monogram (select fonts):</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>The ABC model consists of your first&nbsp;(A), middle (B) and last (C) name, all the same size.</li>
					</ul>
					<h3>ACB monogram (select fonts):</h3>
					<ul>
						<li style="margin-bottom:0;">The ACB model consists of your first (A), middle (B) and last (C) name. 
							The centered, large letter (C) should always represent your last name.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			
