		Each address you instruct us to ship to, including gift-recipient addresses, is considered a separate
		order and is subject to applicable shipping charges.
		<br><br>
		Gift cards are shipped separately free of charge. <br>
		Ralph Lauren Lighting is shipped separately at an additional flat rate of $28 per lamp. Lamps will ship with the base and the shade as 2 separate packages.
		<br><br>
		We ship via the United States Postal Service when you choose the Economy delivery option.  The United States Postal Service delivers packages Monday through Saturday.  We ship via FedEx Home Delivery when you choose the standard delivery option. FedEx Home Delivery delivers packages Tuesday through Saturday from 9 A.M. to 8 P.M. to residential addresses. Orders sent by 2-Business-Day or Next Day shipping methods are delivered Monday through Friday from 8 A.M. to 4:30 P.M. We recommend choosing 2-Business-Day or Next Day shipping if you are shipping your package to a business address.
		<br><br>
		Orders placed with Saturday delivery will arrive Saturday if placed between 11:01 A.M. EST Thursday and 11:00 A.M. EST Friday.   If an order is placed outside of these hours, it will be shipped via the Next Day delivery option.  We do not recommend choosing Saturday delivery if you are placing your order outside of these hours.
		<br><br>
		Ralph Lauren Gift Cards and Ralph Lauren Lighting are not eligible for expedited shipping.
		<br><br>
		Shipments to Alaska, Hawaii, Puerto Rico, US Virgin Islands, Guam, Marshall Islands, Northern Mariana Islands, Samoa and any P.O. boxes are shipped via U.S. Postal Service Priority Mail. Economy, 2-Business-Day, Next Day, and Saturday delivery options are not available. Please allow 5 to 10 business days for delivery. RalphLauren.com is proud to offer shipping to APO addresses. The delivery time for APO shipping may vary.
